  * Starting from gen8, some commands (e.g. STATE_BASE_ADDRESS,
diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/i915/gt/uc/intel_gsc_uc_heci_cmd_submit.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/i915/gt/uc/intel_gsc_uc_heci_cmd_submit.c
